{"tid":2033712,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股票必勝法「及早離去」","createTime":"2020-05-24T22:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T10:47:29.000Z","uid":4740,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7ee491ecfaaffc7c07e3458c116f352bc6a1f6","tid":2033712,"uid":4740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T22:30:14.000Z","msg":"股市原意，乃讓集資搜資有其地，社會向榮，人皆有賺。惜人性貪婪，耗盡心思，巧取豪奪，樂土成煉獄，血雨腥風，殺戳不息，無數人蕩產傾家輸性命，勝者則喪良知人格。<br />\n<br />\n余於股壇數十載，未嘗見一真正鸁者，智者應知此乃一處永無贏家之戰。取勝唯一法︰「及早離去」四字而矣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"8720b74ed93ed09c2c4192b64bd4134e2184a5de","tid":2033712,"uid":127921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T22:35:45.000Z","msg":"菲比斯:?"},{"pid":"73a3e4253e7b43e5370fc27cedef19d430cf1cee","tid":2033712,"uid":317202,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T22:39:12.000Z","msg":"好大火啊 好大火啊"},{"pid":"354597e5960ed3c81e55fa4e449a9d4ffb296122","tid":2033712,"uid":77626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T23:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853bcefc2e3095e381d6f79e38c690b1a1848be1","tid":2033712,"uid":28131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8720b74ed93ed09c2c4192b64bd4134e2184a5de","tid":2033712,"uid":127921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T22:35:45.000Z","msg":"菲比斯:?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T23:52:13.000Z","msg":"叫佢來買港股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963a14e985d50fd6ab3d48ef34b604b8cb55246a","tid":2033712,"uid":156144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"853bcefc2e3095e381d6f79e38c690b1a1848be1","tid":2033712,"uid":28131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8720b74ed93ed09c2c4192b64bd4134e2184a5de","tid":2033712,"uid":127921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"